Introduction

This is a generated document for the Russian Jack Park area. The property tax information data from March 2016 was joined with the geographical parcel data in the Anchorage area and filtered for only parcels within the borders of Russian Jack Park community council.

This document was created to demostrate some of the skils of my business, Alaska Statistical Automation. If you have a project that might be an interesting project I would love to hear about it. Email me at hans.thompson1@gmail.com. Im located in downtown Anchorage.

This document is provided for fun only and should not be used in investment decisions. If you would like to use this data for a futher analysis of investment opportunities, please get in contact! (hans.thompson1@gmail.com)

If you feel there is an interesting visualization that could be done with this information that could add to this report please let me know and I would be happy to try and include it across all areas.

Summary

The Russian Jack Park area contains 1364 residential parcels and 293 non residential parcels. The total taxable residential value of land is $102,469,400 and the total taxable building value is $210,664,600.
The median taxable value for land and structures is $240,100
